## Configuration

### Claude Desktop

Add this to your Claude Desktop config file:

**macOS**: `~/Library/Application Support/Claude/claude_desktop_config.json`
**Windows**: `%APPDATA%\Claude\claude_desktop_config.json`

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "<%= name %>": {
      "command": "python",
      "args": ["-m", "src.server"],
      "cwd": "<path-to-project>"
    }
  }
}
```

